<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Jan1935"><font color="red">18 January 1935</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Helen Joyce): This morning I received a proposal from the London firm which is supposed to be bringing out <i>Ulysses</i>. They want me to compose 735 headlines for the 735 pages e.g. p.1, &lsquo;On the Top of the Tower&rsquo;, p.2, &lsquo;A Morning Shave&rsquo; &lsquo;Theological Talk&rsquo; &lsquo;The Inner Man Satisfied&rsquo; &lsquo;Arrival of the Milkmaid&rsquo;. As Mrs Colm would ask: Can you beat it? </div>
